true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hse1665702715007.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hse1665702715007.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hse1665702715007.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hse1665702715007\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Setup\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Determines whether the Uniface Setup utility is available from the system menu in the title bar.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hse1665702715007__topic_d97436e1_d97437e1_d97438e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hse1665702715007__p_d97439e1_d97440e1_d97441e1\">setup <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Undefined</var> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"hse1665702715007__section_w1112ab1b5b3_w1113ab1b5_w1114ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\"\"</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Undefined. Use default.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The Uniface Setup utility is available from the system menu.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"hse1665702715007__table_d10955e1_d10956e1_d10957e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The Uniface Setup utility is not available from the system menu.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hse1665702715007__section_u33_wbl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d744382e154\">Usage</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hse1665702715007__p_d97445e1_d97446e1_d97447e1\">Dependencies: The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">System Menu</span>\n            property must be <code class=\"ph codeph\">True</code>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hse1665702715007__section_yft_xbl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d744382e169\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hse1665702715007__p_d97451e1_d97452e1_d97453e1\">The Setup utility can be used to change selected\n            initialization settings in <span class=\"ph filepath\">usys.ini</span> without restarting the Uniface\n            desktop application. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kko1705481411881.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kko1705481411881.html\" title=\"The Setup Utility enables users to change selected initialization settings in usys.ini without restarting the application. It can be added to the system menu of an MDI Uniface desktop application.\">Setup Utility</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"hse1665702715007__note_hvd_1cl_4wb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The Setup utility is not available in the Uniface\n            IDE.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hse1665702715007__section_prg_bcl_4wb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d744382e194\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"hse1665702715007__ul_ekd_kcl_4wb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"hse1665702715007__li_d39575e1_d39576e1_d39577e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yye1705472567076.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yye1705472567076.html\" title=\"An application shell is the first object that is executed when a Windows or character mode application is started. It determines how the application is initialized and the first form component that is displayed.\">Application Shells for Desktop Applications</a> (Windows only) </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613575\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613575\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Setup Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Setup Determines whether the Uniface Setup utility is available from the system menu in the title bar. setup = Undefined | True | False Value Description \"\" Undefined. Use default. True The Uniface Setup utility is available from the system menu. False The Uniface Setup utility is not available from the system menu. Usage Dependencies: The System Menu property must be True . Description The Setup utility can be used to change selected initialization settings in usys.ini without restarting the Uniface desktop application. For more information, see Setup Utility . Note: The Setup utility is not available in the Uniface IDE. Applies To Application Shells for Desktop Applications (Windows only) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}